            <Title>自动催化Autocatalysis</Title>
            <Text>From chemistry we learn that certain processes or reactions can speed up on their own when they are combined with a catalyst. The catalyst tends to stabilize the reaction and makes it easier for the process to jump to another level. The catalyst itself usually is not affected by the process and can go on and influence many other reactions. It’s like a couple who wants to get married: The official they enlist to legalize the marriage performs the ceremony but does not enter into the marriage itself.
In autocatalysis, properties, events or products serve as their own catalysts and are “self-breeding.” For example, the invention of the air conditioner created the need for air conditioning, hence the self-stimulated increase in the demand for air conditioners.
In the investing context, this process can be observed in many industries where a competitive advantage is achieved for only a brief period of time. For example, Company A designs a newly automated system allowing it to produce widgets at a greatly reduced cost per unit basis. The lower cost thereby increases demand for the item, creating a profit bonanza for the company. Company A loses its competitive advantage, however, when Company B starts producing widgets in the same manner.
从化学中，我们知道某些过程或反应可以在与催化剂结合时自行加速。催化剂倾向于稳定反应并且使得该过程更容易跳到另一个水平。催化剂本身通常不受该过程的影响并可继续并影响许多其他反应。这就像一对想结婚的夫妻：他们为了婚姻合法化的官员进行了婚礼，但并没有进入婚姻本身。
在自催化过程中，物性，事件或产品成为自身催化剂，是“自我繁殖”。例如，空调的发明创造了对空调的需求，因此对空调的需求自发增加。
在投资的背景下，这个过程可以在很短的时间内获得竞争优势的行业中观察到。例如，A公司设计了一个新的自动化系统，使其能够以大大降低每单位成本生产小部件。较低的成本从而增加了该项目的需求，为公司创造了利润丰厚的财富。公司A失去竞争优势，但是，当公司B以相同的方式开始生产小部件时。</Text>
        </Document>
        <Document ID="BDD9718A-D7B9-4B16-ACF3-C3A546847AA2">
            <Text>The legal system of the nation in which investment occurs must uphold the values of capitalism in order for businesses and markets to work properly. Entrepreneurs and businesspeople need a functioning, ethical, legal framework in place to commit the necessary time, energy and capital to build businesses. Why waste the effort to develop a well-known brand in a country where there is no system in place to protect its trademarks? As a focus investor, you will need to do your homework before investing abroad!
投资所在国家的法律制度必须坚持资本主义的价值观，才能使企业和市场正常运转。 企业家和商人需要一个有效的，符合道德的法律框架来承担必要的时间，精力和资金来建立企业。 为什么要在一个没有制度保护其商标的国家花费精力去开发一个知名品牌呢？ 作为焦点投资者，您需要在投资海外之前做好功课！</Text>
